description:
&lt;p&gt;Circle Bath Hospital (Private Healthcare Provider) is growing and we have an opportunity for a Healthcare Assistance to join the Pre-Assessment Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Circle Health is a company that runs hospitals and health services in the UK. We were founded in 2004, and we are different to most healthcare organisations we build independent hospitals which pioneered five-star hospitality in the UK, and we’re the only organisation running some innovative types of work in the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role &amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated and passionate individual who can work flexibly as part of the hospital’s Pre-Assessment team, to carry out appropriate tasks involving Assisting with COVID swabbing, assessing patients, clinical admin duties, replenishing supplies and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;supporting our team of Registered Nurses in providing and maintaining a care environment of the highest standard to make a positive contribution to the excellence of care and maintenance of the care environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Update the equipment and audits daily and recording samples for the lab.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours - Part time 22.5 per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shifts weekends Friday, Saturday and Sunday&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team worker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Loyalty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Punctuality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional benefits of joining Circle Health:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days’ annual leave with additional days for long-term service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to work scheme: save money on a new bike and benefit from interest-free instalments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private pension scheme helping your to live well in retirement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health and wellbeing programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee assistance programme: get confidential support 24/7&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical insurance to help you get any treatment you need quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-contributory life assurance and income protection insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Parking onsite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free Uniform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season ticket loan: get the benefit of an annual ticket and pay the cost over 12 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
